FBIS3-38802 "drweu026_q_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-026 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Feb 1994 TURKEY Azerbaijan To Use Loan for Construction Project TA0702195594 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1800 GMT 7 Feb 94 TA0702195594 Ankara TRT Television Network Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Announcer-read report over video] [Text] An agreement on the utilization of $10 million of the $15 million loan Turkey has extended to Azerbaijan has been signed in Ankara. The agreement was signed by Azerbaijani Ambassador to Ankara Mehmet Nevruz Oglu and Bulent Ozgun, foreign economic relations director general for the Treasury and foreign trade. Ozgun said the loan will be used in the construction of a Foreign Relations Center to be established in Azerbaijan.
